      "role": "user",
      "content": "I see. It sounds like they've cast a very wide net. You mentioned that the wording can be used to \"hide\" liabilities or catch things I might not anticipate. Are there any other specific terms in there that feel particularly predatory or like they're trying to \"trap\" a person into something they didn't see coming?",
      "source": "evaluator"
